PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1772806277
OL,3,CInteractive map: Who controls my local
OL,4,Ccouncil?
OL,6,FThen there's the City of London - the
OL,7,Fhistoric Square Mile - which is
OL,8,Fgoverned separately by the City of
OL,9,FLondon Corporation which traces its
OL,10,Froots back to medieval times. It works
OL,11,Flike a council, but businesses as well
OL,12,Fas residents get votes in local
OL,13,Felections.
OL,15,FAbove all of this sits the Greater
OL,16,FLondon Authority, led by the Mayor of
OL,17,FLondon. The Mayor handles city-wide
OL,18,Fissues such as transport (through
OL,19,FTransport for London), policing
OL,20,Foversight, fire services, and London-
OL,21,Fwide planning strategy.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
