OL,3,CInteractive map: Who controls my local
OL,4,Ccouncil?
OL,6,FPut simply: boroughs run your
OL,7,Fneighbourhood. The Mayor runs the
OL,8,Fcapital.
OL,10,FBelow is an interactive map showing
OL,11,Fwhich political party controls each
OL,12,Fcouncil. Two of the councils are under
OL,13,Fno overall control:
